\h PASSWORD \d

\uUSAGE\n
!password

\uDESCRIPTION\n
Change your password.
You will be prompted once for your current password, and twice for your new password.
Note that depending on your MUD client, you might not see your passwords as you type them; this is by design.

@p

\uSEE ALSO\n
client, security, set
